data.description: Beautiful two-story home located in El Sendero subdivision. This spacious home features an open concept floor plan with 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. Furnished with ceramic flooring throughout the downstairs, pristine cabinets, stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, carpet throughout the upstairs, outside AC unit bought 2021, new indoor AC unit motor 2020, solar screens on all windows and much more! Conveniently located near Lackland AFB, major highways, restaurants and shopping.
